text: Dzmitry Shershan (born December 28, 1988) is a Belarusian judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 66 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Rishod Sobirov. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Belarus Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:European Games competitors for Belarus Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games
